1
00:00:13,666 --> 00:00:16,333
[ARISTOCRAT A] "The chirping
cries of the insects

2
00:00:16,416 --> 00:00:20,333
over the long night
of the red moon

3
00:00:20,416 --> 00:00:24,541
reminds me of a fleeting soul."

4
00:00:24,625 --> 00:00:27,916
[MASAMUNE crying]

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:30,000
Kamono Yasunori.

6
00:00:30,083 --> 00:00:33,500
He was truly a great man
whom I will miss, dearly.

7
00:00:33,583 --> 00:00:36,666
To think the Onmiyo professor
would become possessed

8
00:00:36,750 --> 00:00:40,041
and then meet a violent
end as a lowly Horror.

9
00:00:40,125 --> 00:00:42,875
I can only imagine
the regrets he had.

10
00:00:42,958 --> 00:00:44,875
That's why we gather
for this poetry reading

11
00:00:44,958 --> 00:00:48,625
and honor only the
good man we knew.

12
00:00:48,708 --> 00:00:52,750
Lord Masamune, I believe
it's your turn to read.

13
00:00:52,833 --> 00:00:56,625
Right. Here's what
I have so far.

14
00:00:56,708 --> 00:01:05,708
"Redder than the red
of the red moon."

15
00:01:10,208 --> 00:01:11,583
[MASAMUNE]
Wait.

16
00:01:11,666 --> 00:01:12,916
Yes?

17
00:01:13,000 --> 00:01:16,083
No, please, I'm sorry for
whatever I did wrong!

18
00:01:16,166 --> 00:01:17,666
[MASAMUNE]
It'll be okay.

19
00:01:17,750 --> 00:01:20,166
I'll be gentle, I promise.

20
00:01:20,250 --> 00:01:22,750
Your first day here?
I haven't seen you.

21
00:01:22,833 --> 00:01:24,041
My Lord, please don't.

22
00:01:24,125 --> 00:01:26,083
[MASAMUNE laughing]

23
00:01:26,166 --> 00:01:27,500
[MASAMUNE gasps]

24
00:01:27,583 --> 00:01:29,500
No! Go away!

25
00:01:29,583 --> 00:01:33,250
[WIFE] You are the worst
husband in the world!

26
00:03:08,416 --> 00:03:09,875
[MASAMUNE]
My wife's a demon!

27
00:03:09,958 --> 00:03:12,125
She's the meanest person
in the whole capital.

28
00:03:12,208 --> 00:03:14,083
Izumi, can you believe
she's banned me

29
00:03:14,166 --> 00:03:16,750
from having any more poetry
readings in my own house?

30
00:03:16,833 --> 00:03:18,333
Happiness is so fleeting.

31
00:03:18,416 --> 00:03:20,166
But she's right to be angry.

32
00:03:20,250 --> 00:03:23,541
You laid hands on a girl during
a gathering to honor a dead man.

33
00:03:23,625 --> 00:03:26,333
That's not true.
I never got the chance.

34
00:03:26,416 --> 00:03:29,000
That jealous old mare had
the nerve to interrupt me!

35
00:03:29,083 --> 00:03:30,875
[IZUMI]
Either way, you're unfaithful.

36
00:03:30,958 --> 00:03:32,875
Now, have you done
your homework?

37
00:03:32,958 --> 00:03:33,750
My what?

38
00:03:33,833 --> 00:03:35,166
Your new poem!

39
00:03:35,250 --> 00:03:37,208
You have been meeting with me
to work on your poetry,

40
00:03:37,291 --> 00:03:38,125
have you not?

41
00:03:38,208 --> 00:03:41,000
Right! How could I forget?

42
00:03:41,083 --> 00:03:42,625
"Redder than the red

43
00:03:42,708 --> 00:03:46,125
of the swollen crimson
moon above my head.

44
00:03:46,208 --> 00:03:49,875
Your flower bud's scent fills
my nose, when I get up close!"

45
00:03:49,958 --> 00:03:51,583
That was terrible.

46
00:03:51,666 --> 00:03:52,958
But it kind of rhymes.

47
00:03:53,041 --> 00:03:54,166
It has bad structure

48
00:03:54,250 --> 00:03:56,458
and obviously
inappropriate metaphors!

49
00:03:56,541 --> 00:03:59,125
We're writing poetry here,
not pornography!

50
00:03:59,208 --> 00:04:00,666
You're a mean teacher.

51
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:04,208
[IZUMI] Masamune, I give you
this lesson not as a teacher,

52
00:04:04,291 --> 00:04:05,708
but as a friend.

53
00:04:05,791 --> 00:04:07,166
After years of marriage,

54
00:04:07,250 --> 00:04:09,958
many things can come between
the nobleman and his wife.

55
00:04:10,041 --> 00:04:12,250
You must learn to
ignore those things,

56
00:04:12,333 --> 00:04:15,458
so you may gaze again upon her
with the eyes of a young man,

57
00:04:15,541 --> 00:04:17,333
the eyes which first saw her.

58
00:04:17,416 --> 00:04:20,833
If you can train yourself to
see her with those young eyes,

59
00:04:20,916 --> 00:04:23,791
your passion for her
will be renewed.

60
00:04:23,875 --> 00:04:25,958
Then putting those renewed
feelings into words

61
00:04:26,041 --> 00:04:27,833
should come easily.

62
00:04:27,916 --> 00:04:30,750
And real poetry will
flow from your pen.

63
00:04:30,833 --> 00:04:32,416
Do you really think so?

64
00:04:32,500 --> 00:04:35,750
Yes. Now go.
We're done for today.

65
00:04:35,833 --> 00:04:37,250
[MASAMUNE chuckles]

66
00:04:37,333 --> 00:04:39,625
An aristocrat who does
not truly love his wife

67
00:04:39,708 --> 00:04:41,416
will move the hearts
of no women.

68
00:04:41,500 --> 00:04:44,041
I don't believe
you believe that.

69
00:04:44,125 --> 00:04:45,625
Ohh...

70
00:04:47,708 --> 00:04:49,708
Happiness is fleeting.

71
00:04:49,791 --> 00:04:53,166
That wandering eye,
how can I stop it?

72
00:04:53,250 --> 00:04:55,250
Oh, I know!

73
00:04:55,333 --> 00:04:56,291
[RAIKOU]
Spy?

74
00:04:56,375 --> 00:04:58,375
[KINTOKI]
On Masamune?

75
00:04:58,458 --> 00:05:00,791
[IZUMI] All I want you to do
is act like house servants

76
00:05:00,875 --> 00:05:02,500
and keep an eye on him.

77
00:05:02,583 --> 00:05:04,666
And if he lays hands
on any servant girls,

78
00:05:04,750 --> 00:05:06,708
report back to me
about it right away.

79
00:05:06,791 --> 00:05:07,875
Why tell you?

80
00:05:07,958 --> 00:05:09,666
We can punish him
right then and there!

81
00:05:09,750 --> 00:05:12,333
You can't ask me to ignore
a man who cheats like that.

82
00:05:12,416 --> 00:05:14,666
I hold aristocrats accountable!

83
00:05:14,750 --> 00:05:18,041
[IZUMI] Masamune is foolish,
but he's not a bad man.

84
00:05:18,125 --> 00:05:20,875
Our families have been close
since our parents were young.

85
00:05:20,958 --> 00:05:23,250
It's important I address
his lack of discipline

86
00:05:23,333 --> 00:05:26,208
without hurting him or
embarrassing his wife.

87
00:05:26,291 --> 00:05:27,708
So please, help me.

88
00:05:27,791 --> 00:05:30,791
Look, Izumi. We have bigger
fish to fry. We can't--

89
00:05:30,875 --> 00:05:33,166
[IZUMI] You two owe me for
all the valuable information

90
00:05:33,250 --> 00:05:34,833
I've given you recently.

91
00:05:34,916 --> 00:05:36,208
[grunts]

92
00:05:36,291 --> 00:05:37,833
[growls]

93
00:05:37,916 --> 00:05:39,958
[chuckles]

94
00:05:40,041 --> 00:05:42,166
[MASAMUNE]
I'm so bored!

95
00:05:43,541 --> 00:05:46,583
This girl never replied to
my invitation to come over.

96
00:05:46,666 --> 00:05:49,000
This girl did come,
but only to slap me.

97
00:05:49,083 --> 00:05:50,708
Oh, and I forgot about you.

98
00:05:50,791 --> 00:05:51,625
[MASAMUNE yelps]

99
00:05:51,708 --> 00:05:57,666
[MASAMUNE snoring]

100
00:06:00,833 --> 00:06:04,791
[IZUMI] Gaze again upon her
with the eyes of a young man.

101
00:06:04,875 --> 00:06:06,666
Put your love into words

102
00:06:06,750 --> 00:06:09,166
and the girl you once fell
passionately in love with

103
00:06:09,250 --> 00:06:11,041
will become your muse.

104
00:06:11,125 --> 00:06:13,708
[MASAMUNE]
The beauty before my eyes

105
00:06:13,791 --> 00:06:17,166
on that day so long ago,

106
00:06:17,250 --> 00:06:21,416
has turned so foul as
to become a monstrosity.

107
00:06:21,500 --> 00:06:23,916
It's no use.

108
00:06:24,000 --> 00:06:25,916
How many naps a
day do you take?

109
00:06:26,000 --> 00:06:28,250
Do you have to do
that right here?

110
00:06:28,333 --> 00:06:30,541
[WIFE] I'm reviewing
our household's budget.

111
00:06:30,625 --> 00:06:33,333
The old servant girl left,
so I hired a new one.

112
00:06:33,416 --> 00:06:36,166
Our kitchen is also in need
of some sort of renewal.

113
00:06:36,250 --> 00:06:37,625
So, I'm going
through our savings

114
00:06:37,708 --> 00:06:40,166
and seeing what improvements
we can afford.

115
00:06:40,250 --> 00:06:41,958
I see right through
her little mind games!

116
00:06:42,041 --> 00:06:44,125
She took away the money
I used for poetry parties

117
00:06:44,208 --> 00:06:46,291
and is now talking of
using it for herself!

118
00:06:46,375 --> 00:06:49,458
She's turning me into
the woman of my own house!

119
00:06:49,541 --> 00:06:51,375
Don't worry about that.

120
00:06:51,458 --> 00:06:53,125
I'll take care of
the household expenses

121
00:06:53,208 --> 00:06:55,333
as soon as I'm
feeling more awake.

122
00:06:55,416 --> 00:06:57,083
That's a lie and you know it.

123
00:06:57,166 --> 00:06:58,833
You spend your free
time playing around

124
00:06:58,916 --> 00:07:00,500
instead of servicing your court

125
00:07:00,583 --> 00:07:03,041
and performing upkeep on
your house and holdings.

126
00:07:03,125 --> 00:07:05,541
Because of this, the budget
is being eaten away.

127
00:07:05,625 --> 00:07:08,625
And don't think it's just money
you need to manage better.

128
00:07:08,708 --> 00:07:09,875
When was the last time

129
00:07:09,958 --> 00:07:11,791
you actually took our
relationship seriously?!

130
00:07:11,875 --> 00:07:12,833
[screaming]

131
00:07:12,916 --> 00:07:14,375
As a young man,

132
00:07:14,458 --> 00:07:17,250
you took pride in everything
you did, public and personal.

133
00:07:17,333 --> 00:07:20,208
You had passion,
ideals, and ambition!

134
00:07:20,291 --> 00:07:23,250
I remember how you would
visit me every night.

135
00:07:23,333 --> 00:07:24,958
Bragging about
climbing the ranks

136
00:07:25,041 --> 00:07:26,875
to bring me wealth and status.

137
00:07:26,958 --> 00:07:28,458
That man... is gone.

138
00:07:28,541 --> 00:07:31,750
Now he just sleeps between
parties and chasing women.

139
00:07:31,833 --> 00:07:34,666
He can't even keep his hands
off his own servant girl.

140
00:07:34,750 --> 00:07:36,250
What a fool I was
to ever believe

141
00:07:36,333 --> 00:07:38,500
a single one of
the lies you told me.

142
00:07:38,583 --> 00:07:40,166
I've even overheard
people call me,

143
00:07:40,250 --> 00:07:43,583
"the wife of the most useless
aristocrat in the capital."

144
00:07:43,666 --> 00:07:47,458
I swear, my pillow now has
more tears than feathers!

145
00:07:47,541 --> 00:07:48,958
But no,

146
00:07:49,041 --> 00:07:51,500
my hurt feelings are just a
symptom of the larger issue.

147
00:07:51,583 --> 00:07:53,041
You've lost your passion,

148
00:07:53,125 --> 00:07:55,375
and the simplest cure to
the problems I've listed

149
00:07:55,458 --> 00:07:56,916
is for you regain it.

150
00:07:57,000 --> 00:08:00,166
I knew coming in here to do
the books would make you angry,

151
00:08:00,250 --> 00:08:02,166
but I also hoped it'd
finally wake you up!

152
00:08:02,250 --> 00:08:03,625
That's enough!

153
00:08:03,708 --> 00:08:05,708
I'm tired of you thinking
you're some innocent martyr!

154
00:08:05,791 --> 00:08:08,041
I am divorcing you!

155
00:08:11,458 --> 00:08:14,041
[WIFE]
You will divorce me?

156
00:08:14,125 --> 00:08:16,000
[yells]

157
00:08:16,083 --> 00:08:20,125
[MASAMUNE groans]

158
00:08:21,416 --> 00:08:24,541
[MASAMUNE] Well, that's a good
reason to keep my mouth shut.

159
00:08:26,375 --> 00:08:27,375
[WIFE]
Where're you going?

160
00:08:27,458 --> 00:08:28,916
[MASAMUNE]
The Light Palace.

161
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:30,416
[WIFE]
What?!

162
00:08:33,708 --> 00:08:35,125
I knew Izumi was crafty,

163
00:08:35,208 --> 00:08:37,541
but I never thought she'd take
advantage of us like this.

164
00:08:37,625 --> 00:08:40,833
I wish we could pay back our
debts by helping anyone else.

165
00:08:40,916 --> 00:08:42,916
Masamune's a dirty old man.

166
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,458
I don't get women.

167
00:08:44,541 --> 00:08:47,666
I just know a Makai Knight
has a duty to repay his debts.

168
00:08:47,750 --> 00:08:49,458
[MASAMUNE]
Turn up here at the corner.

169
00:08:49,541 --> 00:08:51,333
What about the Light
Palace, my Lord?

170
00:08:51,416 --> 00:08:52,625
Change of plans.

171
00:08:52,708 --> 00:08:55,458
I wish to call on
one of my relatives.

172
00:08:58,958 --> 00:09:00,916
[MASAMUNE'S NIECE] Good day.
It's been too far long.

173
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,833
You've become quite
the lovely woman.

174
00:09:02,916 --> 00:09:04,083
[MASAMUNE'S NIECE]
Thank you, my Lord.

175
00:09:04,166 --> 00:09:07,750
I've forgotten, dear,
how old are you now?

176
00:09:07,833 --> 00:09:09,458
I recently turned 14.

177
00:09:09,541 --> 00:09:13,791
Oh! Wonderful!
And you are so cute!

178
00:09:14,833 --> 00:09:17,208
[RAIKOU] I guess everyone's
got family that loves 'em.

179
00:09:17,291 --> 00:09:18,458
[KINTOKI]
Must be his mom's side.

180
00:09:18,541 --> 00:09:20,791
I heard that his father
denounced him long ago

181
00:09:20,875 --> 00:09:21,958
for his antics.

182
00:09:22,041 --> 00:09:23,791
[MASAMUNE'S NIECE screams]

183
00:09:23,875 --> 00:09:26,291
[MASAMUNE]
It'll be okay! Just trust me!

184
00:09:26,375 --> 00:09:27,750
[MASAMUNE'S NIECE]
No, please don't!

185
00:09:27,833 --> 00:09:30,416
Don't worry. I promise
I'll be gentle.

186
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:31,541
[BOTH yelp]

187
00:09:31,625 --> 00:09:32,916
Dirty old man!

188
00:09:33,000 --> 00:09:37,500
No! We can't hurt him!
Izumi said not to, remember?

189
00:09:37,583 --> 00:09:39,041
[MASAMUNE'S NIECE]
Mother, help!

190
00:09:39,125 --> 00:09:40,416
Masamune, no!

191
00:09:40,500 --> 00:09:42,833
What kind of an uncle tries
to defile his own niece?

192
00:09:42,916 --> 00:09:45,416
This is unforgivable!
We're denouncing you, too!

193
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:47,666
[RAIKOU] Well, sounds like
it worked itself out.

194
00:09:47,750 --> 00:09:49,500
[MOTHER A]
No, get away from me!

195
00:09:49,583 --> 00:09:52,458
Don't worry, I promise,
I'll be gentle!

196
00:09:52,541 --> 00:09:53,708
He's... a demon!

197
00:09:53,791 --> 00:09:55,250
[BOTH grunting]

198
00:09:55,333 --> 00:09:57,666
Don't hurt him! We're not
supposed to hurt him!

199
00:09:57,750 --> 00:09:59,458
Don't you wanna clear
our debt to her?

200
00:09:59,541 --> 00:10:01,875
That's all that matters here!

201
00:10:06,750 --> 00:10:07,833
[RAIKOU]
I'm so tired.

202
00:10:07,916 --> 00:10:09,208
We should've told her no.

203
00:10:09,291 --> 00:10:12,250
I mean, it's not like she
can hurt us or anything.

204
00:10:14,125 --> 00:10:16,041
Driver, stop the carriage.

205
00:10:16,125 --> 00:10:18,666
You, girl. Come up
here for a bit.

206
00:10:18,750 --> 00:10:21,291
He's becoming a
full-fledged kidnapper!

207
00:10:21,375 --> 00:10:24,333
Let's drop him off at Izumi's
and let her deal with him.

208
00:10:24,416 --> 00:10:25,500
Move!

209
00:10:25,583 --> 00:10:26,416
'Kay, let's go!

210
00:10:26,500 --> 00:10:27,791
Yes!

211
00:10:27,875 --> 00:10:29,125
[TOWNSGIRL A] No! Get off me!
Please, my lord, no!

212
00:10:29,208 --> 00:10:32,000
[MASAMUNE] It'll be fine,
it'll be fine, relax!

213
00:10:32,083 --> 00:10:32,958
[MOTHER]
Pervert!

214
00:10:33,041 --> 00:10:34,208
[TOWNSGIRL, MOTHER crying]

215
00:10:34,291 --> 00:10:35,875
Don't stop me this time!

216
00:10:35,958 --> 00:10:40,291
But, Raikou, wait. A Makai
Knight can't cut down a human.

217
00:10:40,375 --> 00:10:41,875
[RAIKOU]
Uh...

218
00:10:44,625 --> 00:10:46,125
[WIFE]
Welcome home, dear.

219
00:10:46,208 --> 00:10:47,666
[MASAMUNE]
Hello.

220
00:10:47,750 --> 00:10:49,875
[KINTOKI] And with that, we'll
take our leave now, my Lord.

221
00:10:49,958 --> 00:10:51,750
Please excuse us.

222
00:10:51,833 --> 00:10:53,291
You know, you ruined my day.

223
00:10:53,375 --> 00:10:54,708
Sorry you didn't
get to hurt him.

224
00:10:54,791 --> 00:10:56,666
I'll cook you dinner
to make up for it.

225
00:10:56,750 --> 00:10:58,125
[WIFE]
Don't go just yet.

226
00:10:58,208 --> 00:11:00,916
There's something very important
that I must ask of you.

227
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,875
Would you please tell me
where my husband went

228
00:11:02,958 --> 00:11:04,083
and what did he did today?

229
00:11:04,166 --> 00:11:05,416
[RAIKOU]
What? Oh, lots of things.

230
00:11:05,500 --> 00:11:07,333
[KINTOKI] He, uh,
went to the Light Palace!

231
00:11:07,416 --> 00:11:08,750
I sent someone myself

232
00:11:08,833 --> 00:11:12,250
and he confirmed that Masamune
did not go there today.

233
00:11:12,333 --> 00:11:13,458
Tell the truth.

234
00:11:13,541 --> 00:11:16,833
Where did my husband go,
and what did he do?

235
00:11:16,916 --> 00:11:17,708
Answer me!

236
00:11:17,791 --> 00:11:20,416
[BOTH scream]

237
00:11:22,083 --> 00:11:23,791
She is a demon.

238
00:11:23,875 --> 00:11:25,916
The woman I married...
is a demon!

239
00:11:26,000 --> 00:11:28,708
Who now kicks me
out of my own house!

240
00:11:28,791 --> 00:11:30,458
Happiness is so fleeting.

241
00:11:30,541 --> 00:11:32,000
But her actions make sense.

242
00:11:32,083 --> 00:11:34,083
I warned you about
acting on your passion,

243
00:11:34,166 --> 00:11:36,208
and still, you groped
three girls today.

244
00:11:36,291 --> 00:11:38,916
Not true, I only got
my hands on one!

245
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,208
That's a pretty important
fact you're overlooking!

246
00:11:41,291 --> 00:11:43,083
Hey, knight and squire boy.

247
00:11:43,166 --> 00:11:44,958
