00:21:58,958 --> 00:22:00,666
[RAIKOU]
So what's your point?

490
00:22:00,750 --> 00:22:03,875
[KINTOKI] So, why did
she show up at Izumi's?

491
00:22:06,000 --> 00:22:08,750
[RAIKOU] I guess I should've
asked her about that.

492
00:22:10,000 --> 00:22:11,791
[MASAMUNE]
She's dead.

493
00:22:11,875 --> 00:22:14,750
At long last,
the demon's dead! Tehe!

494
00:22:14,833 --> 00:22:18,833
[WOMEN chattering]

495
00:22:18,916 --> 00:22:21,083
[MASAMUNE]
I'm a free man!

496
00:22:21,166 --> 00:22:23,416
[laughing]

497
00:22:23,500 --> 00:22:26,416
[yelping]

498
00:22:26,500 --> 00:22:28,541
[MASAMUNE]
Freedom is rather painful.

499
00:22:28,625 --> 00:22:30,708
Happiness is fleeting.

500
00:24:03,500 --> 00:24:05,125
[INARI A]
For your master's sake,

501
00:24:05,208 --> 00:24:06,791
for your own sake,

502
00:24:06,875 --> 00:24:09,041
be careful of endless desire,

503
00:24:09,125 --> 00:24:11,833
for it may warp
your personality.

